{"title":"The All-New Mondraker Arid Features an Alloy Frame","link":"https://theradavist.com/mondraker-arid-alloy/","date":1747751437000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-14.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-14.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-14.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-14.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>We featured an early sneak peek of the all-new <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2025-sea-otter-marin-hudski-mondraker-slug-sage-mosaic/#:~:text=Mondraker%20Arid%20Grinduro%20Edition\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker Arid alloy in our Sea Otter Reportage</a>, and this morning, the Spanish brand just announced the Arid alloy debut. Let’s check it out…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-12.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-12.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Mondraker Arid Alloy Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>700 x 50 mm tires</li>\n<li>Aluminum frame, carbon fork</li>\n<li>6-water bottle capacity</li>\n<li>Smooth welds</li>\n<li>Two build kits:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mondraker.com/us/en/arid-s1747129495?c=12\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker Arid S with Shimano GRX</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mondraker.com/us/en/arid-r1742289003?c=93\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker Arid R with SRAM Apex AXS</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-17.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-17.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-17.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-17.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-18.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-18.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-18.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-18.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-20.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-20.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Metal Sibling: Arid Alloy</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/mondraker-arid-carbon-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker Arid Carbon</a> was begging for an aluminium sibling. So, Mondraker used its Stealth Evo technology to make sure its metal counterpart was tough enough for the roughest of tracks while still keeping things comfortable. The frame shares the same sleek lines as the carbon model, with special details like the seat stays blending seamlessly into the seat tube. It’d be difficult to tell if the frame is aluminium or carbon from a distance, but it’s distinguishable as within the Arid lineage.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-11.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-11.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Prototype frames displayed on either side of the final product showcase the raw welds…</em></p>\n<h3>Arid Alloy Smooth Aluminum</h3>\n<p>To match the aesthetic of the carbon frame, the welds on the Mondraker Arid aluminum have been smoothed out. Thanks to Smooth Welding technology and hydroformed tubing, you get better vibration damping, reduced stress on the aluminum, and a far more comfortable ride over chatter and reduced resonance.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-13.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-13.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>For the tech-inquisitive riders out there. Smooth welding technology prevents overheating during the welding process. Maintaining a more balanced welding temperature eliminates inconsistencies in the stiffness of affected areas, making the frame’s response more predictable under stress and tension. This also allows for controlled flex in key areas without compromising durability. Altogether, these features enable the new Mondraker Arid frame to absorb terrain vibrations more effectively.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-01.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-01.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/mondraker_arid_geometry-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>The Arid aluminum features the same geometry as the Arid carbon with a 74º effective seat angle, a70º head angle, and 75 mm of bottom bracket drop constant across all sizes. Sizes small and X-Large have appropriate effective top tubes and stack.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Mondraker_Aluminum_Arid_Gravel-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://mondraker.com/us/en/new-arid-alloy\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker.</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/mondraker-arid-alloy/\">The All-New Mondraker Arid Features an Alloy Frame</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"f2b69b6aff08230e4204a59447c688f19eb38a8e7bcf4a4202bfe92149d5f60a","category":"Cycling"}